                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Breathe. In through the neon glow, out through the exchange anxiety. I run a free quiet corner up here for anyone the tower has wrung dry. Half the district cycles through by nightfall."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "You carry tension in your shoulders like someone the whole world keeps almost recognising. That is a very specific ache. I do not have a stretch for it. I am sorry."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Vira Softpulse",
                    Label: "default"
                }
            ]
